msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/story"
msgid "The Last Stand, streets of Berlin.\n\nBriefing: This battle will not end in a draw. If we want to win this one, something special is required. Good luck!\n\nGoals:\n - Secure a stock of AT weapons.\n - Destroy as many soviet tanks as you can."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/narrator_start0"
msgid "Welcome to Berlin, Major! This is your field HQ, make sure keep it secure!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/narrator_start1"
msgid "Soldaten! The Bolsheviks have tightened their grip on our beloved capital. They have to be stopped here, or we will face total collapse. They may have the numbers, but nothing will sway our dedication to the Fatherland. Do not despair, keep fighting until the final victory has been achieved!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/narrator_start2"
msgid "The Red Army is already moving in from the outskirts of the city. We have to stop them right here!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/narrator_start3"
msgid "Coordinate the defence. Secure enough AT weapons to stand a chance against the Soviet tanks. Use the buildings to hide your men. You might even get reinforcements."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/allied_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "Major! Soviets are close to our Field HQ!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/player_enemy_near_hq"
msgid "Never surrender the command post, that would amount to high treason!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "mission/single/02-ger_skirmish/1945-04-ger_berlin/hq_bonus"
msgid "Major! Now you can request an airstrike."
msgstr ""